<section class="pricing-section" id="precio">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Precio</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Un plan. Sin sorpresas.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Sin contratos, sin tarifas escondidas, sin asteriscos. Cancelas cuando quieras.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card">
      <div class="pricing-badge">Plan único</div>

      <div class="billing-toggle">
        <button class="billing-opt active" data-plan="monthly">Mensual</button>
        <button class="billing-opt" data-plan="annual">Anual</button>
      </div>

      <div class="savings-badge" id="savings-badge" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-5"/></svg>
        16% de descuento
      </div>

      <div class="price-display">
        <span class="price-currency">$</span>
        <span class="price-amount" id="price-amount">199</span>
        <span class="price-period" id="price-period">MXN / mes</span>
      </div>
      <p class="price-sub" id="price-sub">Incluye 14 días de prueba sin tarjeta.</p>

      <ul class="pricing-features">
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Citas ilimitadas — sin tope mensual</li>
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Clientes ilimitados en tu directorio</li>
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Mensajes de confirmación, recordatorio y seguimiento automáticos</li>
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Llamadas automatizadas para no-respuestas</li>
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Campañas de reactivación sin límite</li>
        <li><div class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-6"/></svg></div>Soporte humano por WhatsApp</li>
      </ul>

      <button class="pricing-cta">
        Empezar prueba gratis      </button>
      <div class="pricing-fineprint">Sin tarjeta de crédito · Cancela en 1 clic</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
(function () {
  var opts = document.querySelectorAll('.billing-opt');
  var amount = document.getElementById('price-amount');
  var period = document.getElementById('price-period');
  var sub = document.getElementById('price-sub');
  var badge = document.getElementById('savings-badge');

  opts.forEach(function (btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
      opts.forEach(function (o) { o.classList.remove('active'); });
      this.classList.add('active');

      if (this.dataset.plan === 'annual') {
        amount.textContent = '1,999';
        period.textContent = 'MXN / año';
        sub.textContent = 'Equivale a $166/mes. 14 días de prueba sin tarjeta.';
        badge.classList.add('visible');
        badge.removeAttribute('aria-hidden');
      } else {
        amount.textContent = '199';
        period.textContent = 'MXN / mes';
        sub.textContent = 'Incluye 14 días de prueba sin tarjeta.';
        badge.classList.remove('visible');
        badge.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
      }
    });
  });
})();
</script>
